cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is about natural language processing, specifically dependency parsing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also utilizes deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper conducts experiments on multiple languages, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as well.
